Description: Open Chinese Convert (OpenCC) conversion library - runtime
 OpenCC converts between Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, and
 regional variants (Mainland/Hong Kong/Taiwan) and Japanese Shinjitai
 forms.
 .
 This package contains the shared library needed to run programs
 dynamically linked against libopencc, SOVERSION 1.4.

Package: libopencc-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends:
 libopencc1.4 (= ${binary:Version}),
 libopencc-data (>= ${source:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: Open Chinese Convert (OpenCC) conversion library - development files
 OpenCC converts between Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, and
 regional variants (Mainland/Hong Kong/Taiwan) and Japanese Shinjitai
 forms.
 .
 This package contains the headers, CMake package config, pkg-config
 file, and unversioned shared library symlink needed to build software
 using libopencc.

Package: libopencc-data
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Section: libs
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: Open Chinese Convert (OpenCC) conversion library - data files
 OpenCC converts between Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, and
 regional variants (Mainland/Hong Kong/Taiwan) and Japanese Shinjitai
 forms.
 .
 This package contains the architecture-independent dictionaries
 (.ocd2) and conversion configuration files (.json) used by libopencc
 and the opencc command line tools.

