Package: opencc-jieba
Architecture: any
Section: utils
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 opencc (= ${binary:Version}),
 libopencc-data (>= ${source:Version}),
Description: Jieba segmentation plugin for Open Chinese Convert (OpenCC)
 This package provides the optional Jieba-based word segmentation
 plugin for OpenCC (libopencc-jieba.so) and the merged Jieba dictionary
 and *_jieba.json configuration files it requires. Install this package
 to enable the s2twp_jieba-style configs that use word-segmentation-aware
 regional phrase conversion.
